pan></strong><br />\n<br />\n教育人民 及 加強對內宣傳<br />\nTo educate people and to improve local promotions<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">資源分配 Resources Distribution</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每個廣告預計將使用 1000 - 4000 港元。<br />\nWill designate $1000 - 4000 hkd per ad.<br />\n<br />\n第二期廣告計劃結束後，將向公眾交代成果，跟第一期報告類似。<br />\nAfter stage 2, we will report the results to the public, similar to the 1st stage report.<br />\n<br />\n理應不會有餘額，如有，將轉交星火聯盟。<br />\nIf there's any balance, tho possibly not, we'll donate it to Spark Alliance."},{"pid":"256f7ab03495c764e3c0de962f362fec17f55250","tid":1660054,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4a060412e81aacf2cdaea2b75f21ed15ba9a04","tid":1660054,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"02fff547b2600bf5956846c685987ee84c02db8d","tid":1660054,"uid":181433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f99b5cd40e9a4a2a96a7102099dffa597d95d17c","tid":1660054,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"以往嘅簡單報告：<br />\n測試階段，用$584.92，觸及81457人。<br />\n第一期，用$816，觸及109024人。"},{"pid":"9b41439197ea0f606f156b654e60764d10c04ec7","tid":1660054,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"【行動】西九遊行<span style=\"color: red;\">要大量針對強國人文宣</span>！<br />\n務求<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命</span></strong>！附詳盡策略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659090</a>"},{"pid":"47e56286dae1da821bdafb5ae94a608fbe622695","tid":166005